OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FThe UK asylum appeals backlog has hit
OL,7,Fa new record high and is more than
OL,8,Fseven times the level it was a decade
OL,9,Fago, figures show.
OL,11,FThere were 87,450 cases in the system
OL,12,Fat the end of March, up 72% from
OL,13,F50,976 one year earlier, data from the
OL,14,FMinistry of Justice published on
OL,15,FThursday revealed.
OL,17,FThis is also compared to 11,660 cases
OL,18,Fin the system in the same period in
OL,19,F2016, when current records began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
