OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe backlog refers to the number of
OL,12,Fclaims waiting on the outcome of an
OL,13,Fappeal, where an applicant or
OL,14,Fapplicants has challenged the Home
OL,15,FOffice's decision on their asylum
OL,16,Fstatus.
OL,18,FThe numbers showed that 40% of appeals
OL,19,Fwere successful between January and
OL,20,FMarch this year, a decrease from 43%
OL,21,Facross the same period in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
