OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FThe average waiting time to clear an
OL,7,Fasylum appeal was 67 weeks, up from 54
OL,8,Fweeks in the same three-month period
OL,9,Flast year, the data showed.
OL,11,FEarlier this year, government
OL,12,Fstatistics showed that the backlog of
OL,13,Fpeople waiting for an initial decision
OL,14,Fon an asylum application in the UK had
OL,15,Fdropped sharply to its lowest level in
OL,16,Fmore than six years.
OL,18,FThere were 48,758 people waiting for
OL,19,Fan initial decision on an asylum
OL,20,Fapplication at the end of March 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
