OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FBut the rise in appeals demonstrates
OL,7,Fthe challenges the government faces as
OL,8,Fit aims to end the use of hotels for
OL,9,Fasylum seekers by the next election -
OL,10,Fa pledge Chancellor Rachel Reeves made
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FA report by the Public Accounts
OL,14,FCommittee (PAC), group of MPs who
OL,15,Fscrutinise government spending, warned
OL,16,Fthat the UK's asylum system was on the
OL,17,Fbrink of collapse due to a lack of
OL,18,Fclear strategy last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
