OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FIt found the Home Office was too
OL,7,Ffocused on short-term fixes, and, in a
OL,8,F"shocking and unacceptable state of
OL,9,Faffairs", does not effectively keep
OL,10,Ftrack of where those with failed
OL,11,Fasylum claims have gone.
OL,13,FMany people face being "stuck" in
OL,14,Flimbo at hotels and other asylum
OL,15,Faccommodation while they wait for a
OL,16,Fdecision on their case, the Refugee
OL,17,FCouncil said.
