OL,3,CUK asylum appeals backlog hits all-
OL,4,Ctime high, data shows
OL,6,FThe government announced it would set
OL,7,Fup a new independent body to speed up
OL,8,Fdecision making on asylum appeal cases
OL,9,Fin August, with a 24-week target for
OL,10,Fthe process.
